						<div class="postbody">If you want to get fancy, you could <a href="http://problemkaputt.de/fullsnes.htm#snespputimersandstatus" class="postlink">read from SLHV ($2137)</a> to load the current scanline into OPVCT ($213D), and then display a CPU usage graph. If you start exceeding 192 lines too often, you're in danger of slowdown.</div>

